Glib::IO
========

Perl bindings to the GIO library.

INSTALLATION
------------

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES
------------

Glib::IO requires the following C libraries:

  gio-2.0

and the following Perl modules:

  Glib::Object::Introspection >= 0.014


BUG REPORTS
-----------

Please report bugs to the perl-glib-io product in GNOME's bugtracker:
https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/perl-glib-io/-/issues


